legacy-contents"></span><p> <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:6;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/google-docs/" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/tag/google-docs/">Google Docs</a>中的选项非常相似，不过如果您愿意，您<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:7;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://support.google.com/docs/answer/13951448?visit_id=638290077545746450-2042367713&amp;p=duet-help-me-write&amp;rd=1" data-original-link="https://support.google.com/docs/answer/13951448?visit_id=638290077545746450-2042367713&amp;p=duet-help-me-write&amp;rd=1">可以</a>使 Duet AI 的语气更加随意。有一些选项可以生成部分或整个文档的摘要、使用要点（对于那些<em>Axios</em>粉丝）以及根据您的初始描述创建不同的草稿。此外，谷歌表示您可以使用自定义指令来“优化生成的内容”。文档的“帮我写”工具可以引入<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:8;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-docs-dropdown-menu-feature-announced-162857231.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/google-docs-dropdown-menu-feature-announced-162857231.html">智能画布功能</a>。</p><p>目前，新的虚拟助手仅适用于每位用户每月额外支付 30 美元购买 Duet AI for Google Workspace Enterprise 附加组件的组织。 Duet AI 将在未来几个月内面向中小型企业以及消费者推出，但谷歌尚未透露定价。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/googles-duet-ai-can-generate-emails-and-documents-in- Different-tones-161534645.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/googles-duet-ai-can-generate-emails-and-documents-in-different-tones-161534645.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> aa60727c-efe8-49fa-9847-2d21dbba5d8e</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 30 Aug 2023 16:15:34 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693411601</ingested><modified> 2023-08-30T16:06:44+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category>